column5: Get a load of Mitchel and Glen Shades of deliverance

What do we do fer fun Glen? Ahhh we hunt What else Glen? ahhhh   we fish.. Hell ya,,,,what else do we do Glen? Uhhhh i dunno....  We gonna catch sum bait, so we can catch sum bait, so we can catch sum Gar  Scarey stuff
Choot 'em, choot 'em.  Choot that alliegator....  Classic show.  Watch it every week.

I don't have cable so I have to wtch it on-line via certain not to be mentioned methods, I watched all of the first season in two nights. So please no spoilers for the second season please. What season are they on right now? 2 or 3?
I could watch that all day. Just makes me hungry for some gator.
I've only caught 1 episode. 2/3 guys in a boat got shot (ricochet) by the third guy in the boat. Then they said "we done been lucky today". Or at least what that's what the subtitles said.
What d'ya think of Glen and Mitchell?

What a couple of prizes they were...  They were munching on their favorite supper... Gar pike patties--while smoking cigarettes!  "That little bass wouldn't even fill your hollow tooth"  wow, well done history channel!
yup, its a classic in the making...or maybe not. For Halloween I'm going to give my kid a stuffed gator, a rifle and take away his bathing privileges for the month of October.
